summary: Dogewifangelring - KABOSU, the adorable Shiba Inu who became the iconic face of the Doge meme, has sadly passed away. In her honor, we've created a new decentralized token named "Dogewifangelring," with the ticker symbol $ANGEL. This token represents KABOSU's transition into an angel, symbolized by her wearing an angel ring. Though KABOSU has left us, her spirit remains ever-present in our hearts and in the digital world.
